Qatari Diar Opens Hotel Schweizerhof in Bern After Renovation

-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 
2011-07-03T08:27:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-03/qatari-diar-opens-hotel-schweizerhof-in-bern-after-renovation.html
Qatari Diar Real Estate Investment
Co., the real estate arm of the Persian Gulf country’s sovereign
wealth fund, said it opened Hotel Schweizerhof in Bern,
 Switzerland , after the 150-year-old inn was renovated.  The five-star hotel, located in the Swiss capital’s Old
City, was partially opened April 16 and now all its 99 rooms are
in service, Qatari Diar said in an e-mailed press release.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Robert Tuttle  in Doha at 
 rtuttle@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Harrison at 
 mharrison5@bloomberg.net  